{%- comment -%}
  BKS Studio Archive — exclusive content for Silver+ tier members
  Access guard is handled by the caller (tier check before render).
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="bks-archive-header">
  <p class="bks-archive-eyebrow">BKS Studio Archive</p>
  <h2 class="bks-archive-title">The process. Not the product.</h2>
  <p class="bks-archive-sub">
    What we publish is 10% of what we create. Here is the rest —
    real prompts, discarded patterns, process notes. Personal use.
  </p>
</div>

